About this document

This document was generated using RMarkdown, and the source is available on GitHub at: https://github.com/fmichonneau/evol2015-tweets.

Pull requests to add other figures or fix bugs are welcome.

The dataset used here is available as a CSV file from figshare.

This document (and associated code) is released under a CC0 licence.

If you have questions or comments, I am on twitter at fmic_ or by email at francois.michonneau@gmail.com

Basic summary

  • Total number of tweets with the #Evol2015 hashtag between June 22nd, and July 1st 2015: 6846.
  • Total of original tweets (no retweets): 2614.
  • Number of users who tweeted: 987.
